snippet.title: Cathedral – game intro trailer
snippet.description: Cathedral – an atmospheric sci-fi horror movie in which you have to fight for your life in the last refuge – the Cathedral. Upgrade your character, pick up equipment, fight soulless enemies and defeat a powerful Baron. Repel the inevitable invasion and become a legend of the cosmos!
